verses.text_plain: Now these are the generations of the sons of Noah, Shem, Ham, and Japheth: and unto them were sons born after the flood.
verses.verse_html: 1Now these are the generations of the sons of Noah, Shem, Ham, and Japheth: and unto them were sons born after the flood.

verses.text_plain: The sons of Japheth; Gomer, and Magog, and Madai, and Javan, and Tubal, and Meshech, and Tiras.
verses.verse_html: 2The sons of Japheth; Gomer, and Magog, and Madai, and Javan, and Tubal, and Meshech, and Tiras.

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Gomer; Ashkenaz, and Riphath, and Togarmah.
verses.verse_html: 3And the sons of Gomer; Ashkenaz, and Riphath, and Togarmah.

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Javan; Elishah, and Tarshish, Kittim, and Dodanim.
verses.verse_html:
4And the sons of Javan; Elishah, and Tarshish, Kittim, and Dodanim. ▼
▼ Dodanim: or, as some read it, Rodanim

footnotes.body_text: ▼ Dodanim: or, as some read it, Rodanim
footnotes.body_html: ▼ Dodanim: or, as some read it, Rodanim

verses.text_plain: By these were the isles of the Gentiles divided in their lands; every one after his tongue, after their families, in their nations.
verses.verse_html: 5By these were the isles of the Gentiles divided in their lands; every one after his tongue, after their families, in their nations.

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Ham; Cush, and Mizraim, and Phut, and Canaan.
verses.verse_html: 6And the sons of Ham; Cush, and Mizraim, and Phut, and Canaan.

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Cush; Seba, and Havilah, and Sabtah, and Raamah, and Sabtecha: and the sons of Raamah; Sheba, and Dedan.
verses.verse_html: 7And the sons of Cush; Seba, and Havilah, and Sabtah, and Raamah, and Sabtecha: and the sons of Raamah; Sheba, and Dedan.

verses.text_plain: And Cush begat Nimrod: he began to be a mighty one in the earth.
verses.verse_html: 8And Cush begat Nimrod: he began to be a mighty one in the earth.

verses.text_plain: He was a mighty hunter before the Lord: wherefore it is said, Even as Nimrod the mighty hunter before the Lord.
verses.verse_html: 9He was a mighty hunter before the Lord: wherefore it is said, Even as Nimrod the mighty hunter before the Lord.

verses.text_plain: And the beginning of his kingdom was Babel, and Erech, and Accad, and Calneh, in the land of Shinar.
verses.verse_html:
10And the beginning of his kingdom was Babel, and Erech, and Accad, and Calneh, in the land of Shinar. ▼
▼ Babel: Gr. Babylon

verses.text_plain: Out of that land went forth Asshur, and builded Nineveh, and the city Rehoboth, and Calah,
verses.verse_html:
11Out of that land went forth Asshur, and builded Nineveh, and the city Rehoboth, and Calah, ▼
▼ went…: or, he went out into Assyria
 , ▼
▼ the city…: or, the streets of the city

footnotes.body_text: ▼ went…: or, he went out into Assyria
footnotes.body_html: ▼ went…: or, he went out into Assyria

footnotes.body_text: ▼ the city…: or, the streets of the city
footnotes.body_html: ▼ the city…: or, the streets of the city

verses.text_plain: And Resen between Nineveh and Calah: the same is a great city.
verses.verse_html: 12And Resen between Nineveh and Calah: the same is a great city.

verses.text_plain: And Mizraim begat Ludim, and Anamim, and Lehabim, and Naphtuhim,
verses.verse_html: 13And Mizraim begat Ludim, and Anamim, and Lehabim, and Naphtuhim,

verses.text_plain: And Pathrusim, and Casluhim, (out of whom came Philistim,) and Caphtorim.
verses.verse_html: 14And Pathrusim, and Casluhim, (out of whom came Philistim,) and Caphtorim.

verses.text_plain: And Canaan begat Sidon his firstborn, and Heth,
verses.verse_html:
15And Canaan begat Sidon his firstborn, and Heth, ▼
▼ Sidon: Heb. Tzidon

verses.text_plain: And the Jebusite, and the Amorite, and the Girgasite,
verses.verse_html: 16And the Jebusite, and the Amorite, and the Girgasite,

verses.text_plain: And the Hivite, and the Arkite, and the Sinite,
verses.verse_html: 17And the Hivite, and the Arkite, and the Sinite,

verses.text_plain: And the Arvadite, and the Zemarite, and the Hamathite: and afterward were the families of the Canaanites spread abroad.
verses.verse_html: 18And the Arvadite, and the Zemarite, and the Hamathite: and afterward were the families of the Canaanites spread abroad.

verses.text_plain: And the border of the Canaanites was from Sidon, as thou comest to Gerar, unto Gaza; as thou goest, unto Sodom, and Gomorrah, and Admah, and Zeboim, even unto Lasha.
verses.verse_html:
19And the border of the Canaanites was from Sidon, as thou comest to Gerar, unto Gaza; as thou goest, unto Sodom, and Gomorrah, and Admah, and Zeboim, even unto Lasha. ▼
▼ Gaza: Heb. Azzah

verses.text_plain: These are the sons of Ham, after their families, after their tongues, in their countries, and in their nations.
verses.verse_html: 20These are the sons of Ham, after their families, after their tongues, in their countries, and in their nations.

verses.text_plain: Unto Shem also, the father of all the children of Eber, the brother of Japheth the elder, even to him were children born.
verses.verse_html: 21Unto Shem also, the father of all the children of Eber, the brother of Japheth the elder, even to him were children born.

verses.text_plain: The children of Shem; Elam, and Asshur, and Arphaxad, and Lud, and Aram.
verses.verse_html:
22The children of Shem; Elam, and Asshur, and Arphaxad, and Lud, and Aram. ▼
▼ Arphaxad: Heb. Arpachshad

verses.text_plain: And the children of Aram; Uz, and Hul, and Gether, and Mash.
verses.verse_html: 23And the children of Aram; Uz, and Hul, and Gether, and Mash.

verses.text_plain: And Arphaxad begat Salah; and Salah begat Eber.
verses.verse_html:
24And Arphaxad begat Salah; and Salah begat Eber. ▼
▼ Salah: Heb. Shelah

verses.text_plain: And unto Eber were born two sons: the name of one was Peleg; for in his days was the earth divided; and his brother’s name was Joktan.
verses.verse_html:
25And unto Eber were born two sons: the name of one was Peleg; for in his days was the earth divided; and his brother’s name was Joktan. ▼
▼ Peleg: that is Division

footnotes.body_html: ▼ Peleg: that is Division

verses.text_plain: And Joktan begat Almodad, and Sheleph, and Hazarmaveth, and Jerah,
verses.verse_html: 26And Joktan begat Almodad, and Sheleph, and Hazarmaveth, and Jerah,

verses.text_plain: And Hadoram, and Uzal, and Diklah,
verses.verse_html: 27And Hadoram, and Uzal, and Diklah,

verses.text_plain: And Obal, and Abimael, and Sheba,
verses.verse_html: 28And Obal, and Abimael, and Sheba,

verses.text_plain: And Ophir, and Havilah, and Jobab: all these were the sons of Joktan.
verses.verse_html: 29And Ophir, and Havilah, and Jobab: all these were the sons of Joktan.

verses.text_plain: And their dwelling was from Mesha, as thou goest unto Sephar a mount of the east.
verses.verse_html: 30And their dwelling was from Mesha, as thou goest unto Sephar a mount of the east.

verses.text_plain: These are the sons of Shem, after their families, after their tongues, in their lands, after their nations.
verses.verse_html: 31These are the sons of Shem, after their families, after their tongues, in their lands, after their nations.

verses.text_plain: These are the families of the sons of Noah, after their generations, in their nations: and by these were the nations divided in the earth after the flood.
verses.verse_html: 32These are the families of the sons of Noah, after their generations, in their nations: and by these were the nations divided in the earth after the flood.

tokens.text: and by these were the nations
